Epidemiology of coronary heart disease in HIV-infected versus uninfected 
individuals in developed countries.

Lang S(1), Boccara F(2), Mary-Krause M(3), Cohen A(4).

Author information:
(1)Service de cardiologie, hôpital Saint-Antoine, AP-HP, 75012 Paris, France.
(2)Service de cardiologie, hôpital Saint-Antoine, AP-HP, 75012 Paris, France; 
