Zero-Fluoroscopy Ablation of Accessory Pathways in Children and Adolescents: 
CARTO3 Electroanatomic Mapping Combined with RF and Cryoenergy.

Scaglione M(1), Ebrille E(2), Caponi D(1), Siboldi A(3), Bertero G(3), Di Donna 
P(1), Gabbarini F(4), Raimondo C(2), Di Clemente F(1), Ferrato P(1), Marasini 
