Incidence of haemoglobinopathies in Sicily: the impact of screening and prenatal 
diagnosis.

Giambona A(1), Damiani G(2), Vinciguerra M(1), Jakil C(2), Cannata M(1), Cassarà 
F(1), Picciotto F(2), Schillaci G(2), Cigna V(2), Renda D(1), Leto F(1), 
